ZIPKIN - DISTRIBUTED TRACING

THEORY
api gateway -> distributed tracing server -> database

Monitoring vs observability
Monitoring: reactive.
Observability: proactive, one step above monitoring. Gather data(metrics, logs or traces),
intelligence(AI/Ops and anomaly detection).
OpenTelemetry: Collection of tools, APIs, and SDKs to instrument, generate, collect & export telemetry data(metrics,
logs and traces).

IMPLEMENTATION

1. docker run -p 9411:9411 openzipkin/zipkin:2.32
2. access localhost:9411/zipkin